name: Roots and blooms
description:
To me, taking a picture of someone is like peering into their soul! Watching the beauty and terror in their eyes, in their souls, I want to capture the essence of their souls in my photographs. Especially in this particular photograph, you could feel the soul flourishing!

Gear I used
Camera: Nikon FM10
Lens: 35~70 1:3.5~4.8
Film:Fujicolor C200

Technique: Double Exposure
